that it's tightened,
but it has tightened.

10:07.373 --> 10:09.175 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So that's the first point.

10:09.209 --> 10:14.380 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The second point is that our
50-state poll
underscores the degree to which
Hillary Clinton

10:14.414 --> 10:20.286 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
