10:34.767 --> 10:39.639 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He has to thread the needle, and
she has many
choices and many options, both
in an effort

10:39.672 --> 10:44.544 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to block him in the states he
has to win,
but also to open up the map in
some areas

10:44.577 --> 10:46.312 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
where she's might be able to
expand.

