15:58.891 --> 16:02.862 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But, as you say,
typically
-- and, Dan, I will come back to
you very

16:02.895 --> 16:04.597 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
