16:34.160 --> 16:38.097 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And next, we turn
now to our
periodic look at the major
issues facing the

16:38.130 --> 16:41.067 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
