37:23.575 --> 37:32.584 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now: how the U.S. government is
trying to
stem the tide of terrorism
messages online,

37:32.617 --> 37:35.286 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
