46:12.103 --> 46:18.409 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now we return to Laos, a country
of rich and
deep history scarred by American
bombing during

46:18.442 --> 46:20.244 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
