46:20.277 --> 46:25.616 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Special correspondent Mike Cerre
reports now
from the capital, Vientiane, on
how one American

46:25.650 --> 46:31.956 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
