46:34.325 --> 46:40.031 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIKE CERRE: The first American
president to
address the Lao people, from a
podium decorated

46:40.064 --> 46:45.269 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
with traditional Lao textiles
made by the
first American company allowed
to do business

46:45.302 --> 46:47.104 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
here since the end of the war.

46:47.138 --> 46:52.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAROL CASSIDY, Lao Textiles:
They actually
arrived in Laos, found us and
found something

46:52.143 --> 46:55.446 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
